window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Take an action-packed journey with the Wild Mustang Security Firm where rugged heroes find danger, fiery passion, and unforgettable love. Set in the Wild West, this contemporary collection delivers six thrilling romances full of adventure and suspense.</p> <p>US Marshal John Hampton is skilled at tracking fugitives, but winning the heart of independent Mandy Adams is a challenge. When she resists, he must show her his pursuit is more than just the chase, but about love.</p> <p>Mac McDaniel unexpectedly reunites with his former lover, Willa Reynolds, during a fugitive mission. Willa becomes a key witness under Mac’s protection. Can they overcome their past and find a future together?</p> <p>Billy Croft, a former Navy SEAL, is tasked with guiding photojournalist Finlay Reid through the Grand Canyon. As they face deadly terrain, their fiery personalities clash, leading to undeniable attraction. Can they survive without letting their differences tear them apart?</p> <p>Security expert Noah Taylor yearns for a quiet life, but when journalist Zara Hughes becomes a target of an arms dealer, his protective instincts kick in. Forced together, their opposing personalities challenge everything they thought they wanted. Can they find common ground?</p> <p>Pilot Avery Jackson lives on the edge, but Thom Lyndon is determined to ground her reckless ways. Thom tries to show her love and safety can mix, but can she learn to trust him before her past destroys their chance at love?</p> <p>Christian Reid, undercover to dismantle a terrorist group, finds his mission at risk when Aliya, the enemy’s sister, seeks his help to escape. Their forbidden alliance sparks a passionate, dangerous connection. Together, they must navigate a web of lies and seek justice.</p> <p>The Wild Mustang Security Firm offers heart-pounding adventure, romance, suspense, and passion. Perfect for fans of contemporary Western love stories.</p>"; 
